$5 ({instead of the usual} 7. d3) 7... Bb6 ({somewhat sounder than} 7... Bxb4
8. Qh5 Qd7 9. Bxf7+ $1) 8. a4 a6 (8... a5 $5) 9. d3 Ne7 10. Qh5 O-O 11. Bg5 Be6
12. Nd2 {with slightly the better game for White, but that was at the finish
