({, or} 10... d5 11. hxg4 dxc4 12. Nd2 {(} h5 13. f5 $1 {) is better for White}
) ({, but} 10... Nh6 {(Stohl)} 11. exd6 {(otherwise ...d6-d5)} O-O 12. Nd2 (12.
g4 $5) 12... Bxd6 13. Ne4 Nf5 {is not so clear.})) 10. Bxf7+ $5 {I could not
resist the temptation to land a spectacular blow at this weak point.} ({
However,} 10. fxe5 $1 Nd5 (10... Bg4 $2 11. Bxf7+) 11. Nd2 {(Stohl) was
