23rd USSR Championship, Leningrad 1956)}) ({, and not} 16. Qf4 Bxe4 $1 17. Qxe5
Bg6 18. Qxg7 Qg5+ (18... Qf8 {has also been played}) 19. Rd2 Ke7 20. h4 Qe3 21.
