{The less vigorous} 12. a4 Nf6 13. axb5 axb5 14. Rxa8+ Bxa8 15. Nxb5 cxb5 16.
Bxa8 Bd6 17. g3 O-O 18. Bg2 b4 19. Bg5 Be5 {leads to equality 
