remember that later Pribyl and I spent a long time analysing the game, and we
were joined by Karpov, Vaganian and other players. They were perplexed as to
how I had won so dashingly. They all tried to find a defence for Black, but
every time they were rebuffed, which is not surprising: White's attacking
potential is very great.}) 25... Be7 {This allows a spectacular development of
