Qb8 26. Rbd1 Qd8 27. Rc6 $1 Kg7 (27... Bg7 28. Qe4) ({or} 27... Bg5 28. Qc3+
Kg8 29. Qg3 {is no better}) 28. Qf4 $1 Nb5 29. Rc8 Qe7 30. Rxf8 Qxf8 31. d8=Q
Bxd8 32. Qxf8+ Kxf8 33. Rxd8+ Ke7 34. Ra8 {and 35 a4, winning}) (25... Bd8 26.
Rb3 $1 ({we only looked at} 26. h4 $5) 26... Qa6 27. Qc3+ Kg8 28. Qc2 $1 {(not
allowing the black queen to escape, and threatening Rxg6+)} Rf6 ({it is no
