Rxf1 Bc3 29. Bxc3 Rxc3 30. Qe6+ Kh8 31. Qe7 $1 Rc8 32. Rf7 dxe4 33. Bc4 $1 {
and wins}) 28. e5 {, and White has good compensation for the pawn, but after}
