I suddenly noticed how many people had arrived for our game. And I realised
that I did not have the right to betray their hopes - no, not of victory, but
of an uncompromising struggle.'} 16. h3 {(8)} Rxe3 17. Rxe3 ({After} 17. Qxe3 {
again} f6 {was possible,} ({but I did not like the activation of the black
