43. Qxb7+ Kh6 44. Qxa6 f5 45. Qf6 Qd2+ 46. Re2 Qf4+ {it all ends in perpetual.}
) 35... Nh6 36. g4 $6 {I very much didn't want to allow the knight to go to f5,
but if such weakening moves have to be made, it is clear that the worst is
