37. e4 $1 Rd8 (37... Rd2 38. Qe8 $1) 38. Qf7+) ({, as well as by the merciless
} 35. Bd3+ $1 Kg8 36. b3 $1 {, when the d5-pawn is taboo because of Bc4.})) 35.
Nc3 $2 {(7) A nightmarish reply;} ({White misses an immediate and
