Rxc5 Rf4+ 49. Ke5 Rxc4 50. Rxc4 f2 51. Rc8+ Kg7 52. Rxa8 f1=Q 53. Rg8+ Kxg8 54.
a8=Q+ {with a draw.}) 48. Rxc5 {(11)} Kf6 $2 {(5)} (48... Rxa7 49. Rc8 ({or} 
