) 16. Be2 (16. Bb1 $5) 16... Nxf5 17. Nf4 {, and the 'bad' knight comes into
play.}) (15. cxb5 $6 d5 {is worse for White. --- But Christiansen, like Sax,
was a player with a dynamic style, and he did not like to concede the
