({The goal would have been achieved without particular problems after both} 
22... Rf7 23. b3 Raf8 24. Qg6 (24. Ng3 d5) 24... Rg8 $1 25. Ng3 Bf8 26. Qh5 d5)
({and} 22... Rac8 23. Nf2 Rc7 24. Nd3 Bf6 {with the intention of ...Bg5.}) 23.
