hopes of saving the game. Christiansen will not have a second chance.}) (23.
Qe4 $2 d2 $1 {.}) 23... d2 $1 {(2)} 24. g4 {(22)} ({The mercurial d-pawn
denies White the possibility of playing actively:} 24. f6 $2 Bxf6 $1 25. Nxf6
