Already the decisive mistake.} (16... Be6 $2 {was also bad:} 17. Qe4 $1 Rd8 18.
Bf4 Qc8 19. Ne5 {, since if} O-O {White wins by} 20. Nxd7 Bxd7 21. Bd3 $1 {
(Stohl).}) ({The only chance was} 16... Bc6 {, although after} 17. Bf4 $1 {
White would have retained an obvious advantage:} -- (17... Qxf4 18. Bxc6 O-O-O
19. a4 $1 {with a powerful attack}) ({, or} 17... Qb7 18. Bxc6 Qxc6 19. Re1 $1
