}) (21... Bd6) 22. Rxf6 $1 gxf6 23. Qf5+ Kb8 24. Qxf6 {(Stohl).}) 20. Re1 $1 {
(2)} Bd6 {(12)} ({After} 20... Bf6 21. Re4 {the queen is trapped}) ({while if} 
20... Rhe8 {not only} 21. Rde5 {is strong,} ({but also} 21. Rf5 Qd6 22. Rxf7 {.
})) 21. Rf5 Qc4 22. Re4 ({Even in such a position it is not too late to make a
