20. Qa1 axb2 21. Qxb2 Rxe3 $1 {(Kunin-Veinzettl, Oberwart 2006).}) 18... Rxa3
19. Qb2 (19. Ndb5 Rxe3 $1 20. fxe3 Qe8 {(b6) etc.}) 19... Qa8 {(5) Black has
deployed his pieces well, neutralising the weakness of the d5-pawn, and he is
