energetic, with the idea of} Ne6 19. f4) 18... Ne6 19. Qe4 Qd7 20. exd4 cxd4
21. Nxd4 Rad8 {(Stohl).}) 16. Bd7 $1 Qd8 {(4)} ({Our home analysis concluded
with the variation} 16... Bc8 $2 17. e6 $1 {and wins. But in fact it all
