({In the event of} 11. Nxd5 Qxd2+ 12. Kxd2 cxd5 13. dxe5 Nxe5 14. Nxe5 Bxe5 15.
Bb5+ Bd7 {Black has a sound position:} 16. Rc5 f6 $1 17. Bh4 (17. Bf4 b6) 17...
Bxb5 18. Rxb5 O-O-O {with equality. But White finds an original way of
