simple} 12. Qf5 Nb8 13. Qxc8 {is also possible, but this is probably
insufficient}) 12... Bxf4 13. gxf4 {(threatening Ne5)} Qd8 14. Rg1 {with the
initiative. --- Here Black has to defend, whereas Karpov wanted active
