Bf4 c5 11. g3 $1 {Karpov obviously did not like this move.} ({Apparently he
was hoping for the routine} 11. e3 {, when after} c4 ({or} 11... Rc8 12. Qa4 c4
{he could have created counterplay. Now, however, the threat of Bh3 reminds
